freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Have had a fever up to 106 degrees, thought the fever was r/t the vaccine at first, but was then diagnosed with UTI and pyelonephritis

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Spoke with my PCP yesterday and he ordered a CMP, CBC, UA, antibody test, and another Covid Nasal Swab. Because my symptoms are keeping me from working. No results yet- will be next week and I'm miserable!!! No one from the CDC has called me!!
